# Layout: host embedded (prefijo Sogna/)
# ==============================================================================

# --- TIER 1: Secretos (defensa en profundidad) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
**/memory/operational/vault/
credentials/
